            <formatted-text>
              <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>What airlines and phases of flights are responsible for the majority of crashes?</run>
              <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
              <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>We see that </run>
              <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>1) </run>
              <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Asiana</run>
              <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> should be careful about their </run>
              <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>approaches</run>
              <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;</run>
              <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>2) </run>
              <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>Atlantic Southeast</run>
              <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'> should be careful about their </run>
              <run bold='true' fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>climbs</run>
            </formatted-text>
            <top-left>
              <visual-coordinate class='axis'>
                <x-coord cell-offset='0.0257143'>
