                    </capturedDeltas>
                  </story-point>
                  <story-point caption='However, once we focus on fatal injuries, we realize that fatal injuries are more common outside the US despite there being less datapoints outside the US. We cannot verify this with the current dataset, but this is presumably due to such flights being long and traveling over water.' captured-sheet='Global Heatmap of Crashes II' id='4'>
