                              <run fontalignment='0'>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                              <run fontalignment='0' fontcolor='#000000' fontname='Benton Sans Book'>We cannot verify this with the current dataset, but this is presumably due to such flights being long or having to travel over water.</run>
